404
00:19:21,530 --> 00:19:22,440
Thank you, Your Highness.

405
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:33,070
I am sorry.

406
00:19:33,070 --> 00:19:34,710
I lost hold of it.

407
00:19:35,090 --> 00:19:36,020
Seems like

408
