430
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:59,000
What a pity!

431
00:21:01,660 --> 00:21:02,800
It is a pity.

432
00:21:11,430 --> 00:21:14,480
Cold Ice, I just realize

433
00:21:14,710 --> 00:21:16,310
