434
00:21:20,580 --> 00:21:21,370
Cheers.

435
00:21:38,900 --> 00:21:41,180
Please stay, Your Highness.

436
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:43,020
I am in good mood today.

437
00:21:43,020 --> 00:21:44,830
I’ll walk you out.

438
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:46,670
Since you don’t want

439
00:21:46,780 --> 00:21:48,630
