448
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,750
Smart guy.

449
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:09,920
Why can you

450
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:10,790
figure out everything?

451
00:22:11,580 --> 00:22:13,660
Fine. There you go.

452
00:22:13,660 --> 00:22:14,800
Without your help,

453
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:15,760
