454
00:22:31,580 --> 00:22:32,310
You are back?

455
00:22:39,570 --> 00:22:40,260
How was it going?

456
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:42,270
Did you see Chun?

457
00:22:45,170 --> 00:22:46,120
How do you know?

458
00:22:48,010 --> 00:22:49,520
I don’t know anything.

459
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:57,390
You and Her Grace made the decision

460
00:22:57,760 --> 00:22:59,250
to marry Chun to me?

461
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:03,060
Yes.

462
00:23:04,220 --> 00:23:04,870
I did.

463
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:09,670
It’s none of your business.

464
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:15,070
What? You don’t like her?

465
00:23:26,290 --> 00:23:27,640
She is a smart girl

466
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:28,660
from the imperial family.

467
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,060
Why don’t you like her?

468
00:23:32,290 --> 00:23:34,680
No reason.
I’m just not good enough for her.

469
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:39,270
For Chu Qiao, right?

470
00:23:42,270 --> 00:23:43,110
Yuwen Yue,

471
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,260
let alone

472
00:23:45,450 --> 00:23:46,680
