484
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:15,240
with Yan Xun alone

485
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:16,150
for three years.

486
00:24:16,320 --> 00:24:17,120
They could have done

487
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:18,180
what they wanted.

488
00:24:18,380 --> 00:24:19,520
