504
00:24:53,490 --> 00:24:54,560
only because of his own suspicion.

505
00:24:54,560 --> 00:24:55,790
I would never agree.

506
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:57,750
But now,

507
00:24:57,890 --> 00:24:59,910
Yan Xun is full of hatred and rage.

508
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:01,650
If he succeeds in

509
00:25:01,650 --> 00:25:02,800
leaving Chang’an,

510
00:25:02,800 --> 00:25:04,690
