511
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:06,280
The North will never be in peace.

512
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:09,930
As a prince and general,

513
00:25:09,930 --> 00:25:10,760
I will never allow it

514
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:11,890
to happen.

515
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,000
Yuwen Yue,

516
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,000
