in different ministries of Chang’an.

530
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:58,510
I don’t think we’ll be stopped.

531
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:00,360
If we can’t go out of the gate,

532
00:26:00,730 --> 00:26:01,750
