533
00:26:02,050 --> 00:26:03,460
will work.

534
00:26:06,450 --> 00:26:08,550
Seems like we can only succeed
through disturbances.

535
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:10,230
By then,

536
00:26:10,610 --> 00:26:12,140
we’ll make some disturbances

537
00:26:12,690 --> 00:26:13,700
to draw the attention of guards

538
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:14,610
who defend the city walls.

539
00:26:15,240 --> 00:26:18,570
