547
00:26:40,380 --> 00:26:41,360
I hear

548
00:26:41,670 --> 00:26:42,760
the Crown Prince of Liang

549
00:26:42,910 --> 00:26:44,460
hasn’t used anything

550
00:26:44,460 --> 00:26:45,410
that has been touched by men

551
00:26:45,410 --> 00:26:46,500
