555
00:26:52,210 --> 00:26:54,120
There is

556
00:26:54,350 --> 00:26:55,600
even a land

557
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:57,350
in his palace

558
00:26:57,350 --> 00:26:58,030
where some young girls

559
00:26:58,030 --> 00:26:59,600
